title: Day 3 Lay Day Waikiki - 2016 Rip Curl GromSearch International Final
description:
With a declining swell at Ala Moana Bowls the GromSearch International Final was put on hold for the day, which gave the groms a lay day to experience the local culture of Honolulu.

Artist: jonathankrisp
Track: All Your Favourite Super Heroes
Source gettyimage
